To set a variable

VARIABLE=setting
(make sure no space in between!)

Use "sync" to save monitor variables to the NVRAM



PS1=rommon ! > 
FPGADNLD=1
TFTP_SERVER=223.255.254.254
IP_SUBNET_MASK=255.255.0.0
DEFAULT_GATEWAY=1.14.0.1
IP_ADDRESS=1.14.0.118
?=0
TFTP_FILE=ytse/ifs-palmbeach.bin




r=repeat
h=history
?=help
b=boot
ls=dir
i=reset
go=tftpdnld

